[30;1m1460 | [0m[35m#### Features {: #3.57.0-rest-api-feature }[0m
[30;1m1461 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m1462 | [0m[35m- Added the ability to save task's diagnostics data as artifacts. These artifacts are available at t[0m
[30;1m1463 | [0m[35m  task's detail endpoint. To download them, issue a GET request to `${TASK_HREF}profile_artifacts/`.[0m
[30;1m1464 | [0m[35m  The artifacts are cleaned up automatically by the orphan cleanup.[0m
